{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_01_02",
  "title": "神崎莉央 2話 気高く咲き誇りたい",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、貴方……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ it’s you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "挨拶しようと探したんですけど、迷ってしまって\nライブ、成功おめでとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wanted to find you and say hello‚ but I got lost.\nCongratulations. That was a great performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.803540923720911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 9.93884341716766
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "……本当に来るなんて思わなかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I didn’t think you would actually come.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.938843417167664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_evening",
      "startTime": 13.655510083834331
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirの神崎莉央から書留？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A letter from LizNoir’s Rio Kanzaki?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.705510083834334,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 719.999999999997,
          "startTime": 15.42551008383433
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "この間のシュークリームのお礼に\n私達のライブチケットを送ります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for the cream puff the other day.\nAttached a ticket to LizNoir's next live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.830510083834337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "良かったら勉強においで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hope you find it instructive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.55550998846691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 26.8555099885
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 26.8555099885
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "……嫌みの通じない男ね\nそれともワザとかしら……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t understand sarcasm‚ do you.\nOr was it intentional?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.4555099885,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 32.2888433218
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "どうかしましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is something wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.28884332180024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "なんでもないわ\nここでは目立つから入って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ nothing.\nCome in. We shouldn’t stand around here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.3388433099,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3419.999999979311,
          "startTime": 38.75884330987931
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 38.4730947137
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 38.4730947137
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "で、私達のライブの感想は？\n本気の私達を観たら諦めが付いたでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ what did you think of our performance?\nHave you decided to give up after seeing us on stage?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.97217664321264,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 46.2721766432126
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "貴方の担当アイドルが私達を追い抜いて\nトップに立つなんて絶対に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your idols will never overtake us\nto stand at the top…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.33884330987932,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 52.22141265273097
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、凄く良かった。こんなに興奮したライブは\n久しぶりです。最後は仕事を忘れて声を出してました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was amazing! I haven’t had such a great live experience in a while.\nTowards the end‚ I was cheering out loud‚ forgetting that I was here for work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.3880793194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 60.75474598606428
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "――え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.75474598606428,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2466.666666666669,
          "startTime": 63.22141265273095
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "私達は愛想を振りまいたり、媚びを売ったりしません\nそんな形でアイドル界の頂点に立つつもりはない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We don’t sell ourselves out and butter up to people.\nThat’s not who we are or who we want to be.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.32141265273096,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirはパフォーマーです\n私達は……歌とダンスで頂点に立ちたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re performers here at LizNoir.\nWe want to reach the top with song and dance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.3547459861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "気高く咲き誇りたいんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s who we are‚ and we’re proud of that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.31746313396624,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 733.3333333333485,
          "startTime": 83.05079646729959
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（LizNoirのライブは本当に凄かった）\n（クールで観客に媚びないスタイルだけど）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(LizNoir’s live was really impressive.)\n(They play it cool‚ never catering to the fans.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.0802068454378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（しっかりと実力が伴っているから、強気の発言でも）\n（あれだけ支持を集められんだろうな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But they back up that attitude with legitimate ability‚)\n(which is why they have so much support.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.1501168459,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（今のアイドル業界を見渡してみても）\n（稀有な存在なのは間違いないか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(There aren’t many like them)\n(in this industry.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.050116846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 104.11678351262056
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "……ヤケに素直じゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re so quick to praise us….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.18345017928723,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 107.09823472995404
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "いいの？　私達は貴方のライバル――敵なのよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Have you forgotten that we’re rivals—enemies?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.09823472995404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そうかもしれませんが、価値のあるものは\n敵味方関係なく正当な評価を受けるべきです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That may be so‚ but credit should be given where it’s due‚\nwhether we’re on the same side or not.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.9649015874,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 118.70714826406953
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "そう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.70714826406953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "……他の事務所なのに\nこんな人は初めてだわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But from a rival agency…\nI’ve never met someone like this before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.8071482641,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 125.1404815974029
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_02-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "私を油断させるためにわざと……？\nでも、この人はそんなに器用には見えないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is he trying to trick me into letting my guard down?\nBut he doesn’t look that clever…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.37381493073627,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 131.94048159740294
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
